    <p>Developed by a professional in his FREE TIME since the beginning of 2015!</p>
    <p>This site is very security minded! All communications are encrypted, and your password is stored using non-reversible encryption.
    <p>Please e-mail me at admin@hearthdrafter.com with your feed-back and/or questions!</p>
    <p>This is a very early alpha release. Expect more features and bug fixes incoming!</p>
